{"tid":992872,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點食雞中翼？","createTime":"2019-01-23T13:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T14:55:37.000Z","uid":126072,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bb4d37eb1636c2c3b8b37f757695cd2422f784a1","tid":992872,"uid":126072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:11:46.000Z","msg":"我首先𡁻左頭同尾尾既軟骨<br />\n之後食幼骨個邊既肉<br />\n食乾淨就到粗個邊<br />\n應該係最佳食法啦掛"},{"pid":"9e78e52cf156581b72b03bb840df885e218b470a","tid":992872,"uid":198401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:12:42.000Z","msg":"一啖吞咗佢"},{"pid":"14a668907ead562c0a0500a691d211975f428f7e","tid":992872,"uid":232594,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:16:59.000Z","msg":"咬走頭尾軟骨先，然後食兩邊d肉，跟住咬走條細骨，食埋淨底d肉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732157cda6e0810c98242d7b547007c6f700c216","tid":992872,"uid":145927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"食左頭尾嘅軟骨先，再抽兩條幼骨出嚟，最後掉左啲肉淨妹骨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56f19e2710b1b913e6429d4ef2a3cb23edeaf6a","tid":992872,"uid":108756,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"細個好鍾意食雞翼 依定睇到呢個post先醒起原來自己由細都用同一套食法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會食左有返皮突出黎個邊先 跟住第第二邊 跟住食上邊（皮個邊）啲肉 最後另一邊啲肉 再慢慢食清佢 但從來唔會成隻放入口妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4f5870ec44bb0fc7903add0dedd87e8f6003aa","tid":992872,"uid":58867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:50:34.000Z","msg":"連骨食埋"},{"pid":"950ca0e3c40eedc2d8d0c26af85260305af61d8e","tid":992872,"uid":202051,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:57:24.000Z","msg":"假設由一件雞翼正上方望<br />\no&lt;=====&gt;o<br />\n食左上下兩邊啲肉<br />\n然後面頭塊皮同底下<br />\n然後中間就筷子挑黎食<br />\n唔咬軟骨 我覺得好核突"},{"pid":"c8712270143a04ae8d743694c3599eae06c8783e","tid":992872,"uid":227026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"連骨食"},{"pid":"0889e6acb362c529d0cd250a8835997ad0817b90","tid":992872,"uid":225996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:32:51.000Z","msg":"食咗多皮個邊先，然後咬兩邊軟骨，最後乾乾淨淨咁食埋啲肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3461e0a149f36a098dd0233ba6333458400912d","tid":992872,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"食頂頭嘅肉先<br />\n然後起一條骨<br />\n再圍住剩返嗰條骨不停「損」<br />\n最後咬埋軟骨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf28abc4f4762c5d83a0c1872a3f0d40bdf5b010","tid":992872,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:55:11.000Z","msg":"撕開層皮<br />\n拆哂啲肉<br />\n再食條骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0060f8b5f7f7c947b18f7cb3b72ce4f1be0c2b5","tid":992872,"uid":196014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:55:37.000Z","msg":"淨係食肉<br />\n層皮撩翻岀嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}